parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Erratic Speedometer and Instrument Cluster Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the speedometer and instrument cluster can cause the driver to lose track of their speed, leading to accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The speedometer needle sticks or freezes
shows incorrect speeds
or does not work at all. Other instrument cluster gauges
such as the oil gauge
fuel gauge
and warning lights
may also malfunction or become erratic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause fires, leading to vehicle damage or loss, and potentially harm occupants.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences electrical issues
such as faulty wiring
overheating components
or short circuits
which can lead to fires or other safety hazards.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Air Conditioning and Heating System Failures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning and heating system can cause discomfort, distraction, or even health risks to occupants.
symptoms: The air conditioning or heating system malfunctions
causing extreme temperatures
smoke
or odors to emanate from the vents.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission and Gear Shift Indicator Failures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and gear shift indicator can cause loss of control, accidents, or traffic violations.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
and the gear shift indicator light does not function or is dim
making it difficult to determine the vehicle's gear position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition and engine system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The engine stalls or hesitates
and the ignition system malfunctions
causing the vehicle to lose power or shut down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of brake lines can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
loss of brake pressure
brake fluid leaks
rust or corrosion on brake lines
sudden failure of brakes while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dynamic electronic brake system can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
loss of brake pressure
sudden failure of brakes while driving
brake booster light is on
fuel smell while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal goes to the floor
loss of brake pressure
sudden failure of brakes while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear indicator can cause the driver to be unaware of the gear the vehicle is in, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The gear indicator on the instrument panel does not illuminate
making it impossible to know which gear the vehicle is in.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the 4WD system can cause the vehicle to shift unexpectedly, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The 4WD system malfunctions
causing the vehicle to shift into 4LO or neutral without warning
and the service 4WD message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The transmission slips and jerks
causing the vehicle to lose power or stall
and the driver may experience a loud clunk or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failure can cause various systems to malfunction, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The electrical system fails
causing the blower motor to stay on even after the car is shut off
and the airbag sensors may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt release button can cause passengers to be trapped in an emergency situation.
symptoms: The seat belt release button is hard to unlock
making it difficult for passengers to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
